data.description: Must see 2-story, in a great Loveland location - close to shopping, restaurants, schools and easy access to I-25. The kitchen perfectly flows into the dining/living rooms and offers slab granite countertops, newer stainless-steel appliances with gas range (all included), ample upgraded cabinets and a large walk-in pantry. Upstairs you will find the generously sized primary suite, with 2 closets, a luxurious 5-piece bath and direct access to the conveniently located laundry room. Additionally, there are two more bedrooms upstairs, along with a secondary bath and loft - great for an office, study, or second living space. The fully fenced backyard is ready for entertaining with the over-sized patio, full sprinkler system and hot tub. You will have plenty of space to store all your toys in the oversized, 3-car garage with service door. The full unfinished basement is ready for your personal touches and future expansion. HOA offers a community pool, hot tub, clubhouse, fitness center as well as weekly trash and bi-weekly recycling pick up. Schedule your showing today!
